│ in `<true, true, true, true>`.                                                             │
│   - This leads to an incorrect final result of `1`.                                        │
│                                                                                            │
│ The miscompilation occurs because the vectorizer incorrectly changes a `zext`              │
│ (zero-extension) to a `sext` (sign-extension) when vectorizing the `freeze` instruction's  │
